The Harvester:
A reconnaissance tool used to collect emails, subdomains, domains, and IP addresses from public sources.
SYNTAX:
1️⃣ Extract Emails & Subdomains using Bing
theHarvester -d ibm.com -b bing
2️⃣ Extract Emails using LinkedIn
theHarvester -d ibm.com -b linkedin
3️⃣ Save Results to a File
theHarvester -d ibm.com -b bing -f ibm_results
