SHERLOCK:
Sherlock – A tool used to find a specific username across 500+ social media platforms.
Using Sherlock, you can search a username across many social media sites.

1️⃣ Search a Username
python3 sherlock username

Example:

python3 sherlock vijay
2️⃣ Save Results to a File
python3 sherlock vijay --output results.txt
🔎 Check the Results

You will see:

✅ Where accounts exist (valid profiles)

❌ False positives (site shows username but account may not exist)

Example output:

[+] Twitter: https://twitter.com/vijay
[+] Instagram: https://instagram.com/vijay
[-] Facebook: Not Found
