VIEWDNS
A web tool used to view DNS records, IP information, and domain details of a "website"
SYNTAX:
1️⃣ Find DNS records
dig ibm.com
2️⃣ Find Name Servers
dig ns ibm.com
3️⃣ Find Mail Servers
dig mx ibm.com
4️⃣ Reverse IP Lookup
host 8.8.8.8
